title: Israeli, Polish presidents march to commemorate Holocaust victims
text:
Israeli, Polish presidents march to commemorate Holocaust victims 4:51pm BST - 01:05 
The annual 'March for the Living' takes place at the former Auschwitz-Birkenau death camp in memory of the victims of the Holocaust. Rough cut
